Semana 2: 
clear
  Command used to clear the terminal screen  
sudo apt install "INSERT APP NAME"
  Syntax use to install a packet when the its name is already known
  Example: sudo apt install build-essential
sudo apt search
  Syntax use to search available packages

lsb_release 
  To obtain information about the Linux distribution
  Example: 
  lsb_releasea: to show all information

uname
   To obtain kernel information and processor information
   Example: 
   uname -a: to show all information

mkdir "INSERT NAME"
  Use to create or make new diorectories
  Example
  mkdir Documents

ls
  Listing about files in current directory
  Example:
  ls -l: to show more information
